Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Input sequences of single-particle indices", "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8874562566990304`*^9, 3.887456258704954*^9}, {
  3.8883150838482122`*^9, 
  3.8883150934469776`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"b9ff103f-8cfe-47ef-b956-\
18a2634e64bc"],

Cell["\<\
Loading of the 8 (4) input sequences of single particle indices, \
corresponding to left-and-right-dressed Feynman diagrams of disjoint direct \
type with two non-identical (identical) one-body interaction vertices. \
Contributions with non-identical vertices are twice the ones generated by two \
identical vertices, as the former do not possess any vertex permutation \
symmetry and hence have multiplicity equal to one.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8883151027747664`*^9, 3.888315139028142*^9}, {
  3.888407377730768*^9, 3.888407378817301*^9}, {3.8928031069237204`*^9, 
