\>", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.888315861110175*^9, 3.8883159051561947`*^9}, {
  3.8983468473701744`*^9, 
  3.8983468556580143`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"a6596a65-0d43-43fa-ac30-\
285abbfacb19"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Times are sorted in ascending order: \[OpenCurlyQuote]4\[CloseCurlyQuote] \
is the latest time and denotes t, \[OpenCurlyQuote]3\[CloseCurlyQuote] \
denotes ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["t", "1"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "5e2e3441-91f0-4f7c-958a-819292b6a116"],
 " and  \[OpenCurlyQuote]2\[CloseCurlyQuote] denotes ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["t", "2"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "ac53fb35-4b23-4f09-8e11-345ac3e82664"],
 " . The earliest time is \[OpenCurlyQuote]1\[CloseCurlyQuote] and denotes t\
\[CloseCurlyQuote]."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8883167440333986`*^9, 3.88831696819341*^9}, {
